{"tid":1394856,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「焦土」我們可以尋找的最大盟友-索羅斯","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T20:11:24.000Z","uid":29132,"like":77,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a5993594c1413743f707c7e83f2b08c972ccde6a","tid":1394856,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OirOkR7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOirOkR7.png&h=c1021126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n著名國際投資者索羅斯（George Soros）出席瑞士達沃斯（Davos）世界經濟論壇（World Economic Forum）時警告，中國擁有先進的監控科技，令國家主席習近平成為自由開放社會「最危險的對手」。<br />\n<br />\n索羅斯表示，「中國不是世界上唯一的獨裁政權，但它是最富有、最強大、技術最先進的政權。這令習近平成為開放社會最危險的對手。」他警告指，中國可能利用人工智能和機器學習，以加強國內監控，形容是「前所未有的危險」。<br />\n<br />\n他又批評美國總統特朗普對中國的立場，認為對方不應該與幾乎全球所有國家發動貿易戰，而應該聚焦中國。他敦促華府打壓如華為、中興通訊等的中國科技公司，批評這些公司為其他國家帶來「不可接受的安全風險」。<br />\n<br />\n富甲一方的索羅斯，旗下的開放社會基金（Open Society Fund）有指是現時全世界最大規模的「慈善機構」，資助全球各地不少非牟利組織，輸出「自由民主」的西方意識形態。不過組織本身亦被匈牙利、俄羅斯等國批評干預國內政治而受狙擊。<br />\n<br />\n開放社會基金會（英語：Open Society Foundations，縮寫為 OSF），前身為開放社會研究所（Open Society Institute），非盈利研究機構，由喬治&middot;索羅斯捐款成立。其目標在於形成政策，以推進左翼自由主義、進步主義、民主政治、人權、經濟、法律及政治上的改進，增進公民參與，以形成公民社會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.opensocietyfoundations.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opensocietyfoundations.org&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEdC8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=64f6c31f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.opensocietyfoundations.org</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正常：佢可以成為強大嘅外國勢力<br />\n焦土：唔知佢有冇興趣嚟多次金融風暴呢，或者教一教路我地香港市民自製金融風暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"c6c5eaef2856e65345737481130844e804e0f352","tid":1394856,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a9fff64edd8c23c19adb1615998574fed0583a","tid":1394856,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:32:00.000Z","msg":"認真，市民自製金融風暴有冇可能？"},{"pid":"d5587741460b0f0dc7dc676c588344039469c343","tid":1394856,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=QWSXAyybcV8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3DQWSXAyybcV8&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEdC8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=1f107c30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=QWSXAyybcV8</a><br />\n<br />\n車勁啲定盾牌陣勁啲"},{"pid":"33fadffc291b44cffa34a4b14ed5a71b75a1b975","tid":1394856,"uid":81424,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a5a9fff64edd8c23c19adb1615998574fed0583a","tid":1394856,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:32:00.000Z","msg":"認真，市民自製金融風暴有冇可能？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:38:02.000Z","msg":"如果有大量市民冒住<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">民意</span></strong></span>同<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">犯法</span>嘅風險襲擊中資銀行<br />\n令到全港市民對中資銀行失去信心<br />\n繼而𢹓提<br />\n就會製成金融風暴<br />\n<br />\n利申唔建議示威者咁做 民意真係有機會逆轉"},{"pid":"be0608c87385bcbdb67c8574f0ab012c041b7afb","tid":1394856,"uid":125029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"同我瘋狂推爆「公務員事務局」FB Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394653</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"92cc26b66c87991480d05c7fd613145ba1b4513e","tid":1394856,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:4